  <h3>About</h3>

                <p>Laravelsnippets.tk is a simple repository of useful snippets for Laravel framework. It allows users to submit or grab useful code snippets. It's primary goal is to help developers make their work faster and easier by providing code samples with guides which are ready to be grabbed anytime and anywhere as long as you have internet access. In laravelsnippets.tk, developers can share code with each other easily. Happy coding web artisans! </p>

